main event: Two round, white objects, the size of baseballs, were observed moving together some distance apart.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for about 5 minutes., The objects were described as being round and white., The observer was stationed at a drive-in and happened to look at the horizon., The conditions were cloudy with sprinkling rain and visibility of 2 miles., The conclusion drawn was that the objects were likely reflections of lights due to weather conditions.
witness description: a student working at a drive-in
